Requirements :

Python 3.x with :
	Flask
	Matplotlib
	Numpy
	Tkinter
	smtplib
	multiprocessing
Email accounts for all voters
Server with internet access


Usage

(Cube may not be updated automatically. Drag mouse or press any key to show current status)

1.Open a command prompt. Navigate to the project folder (titled code).
	Linux :  python vote.py
	Windows :  py -3 vote.py
In the command prompt, enter email addresses

2. In any browser, Open localhost:5000

3. Enter votes as sent to email addresses

4. Press Finalize Voting on the Cube GUI. 

Incorrect voting results in an unsolved cube
Correct voting results in a solved cube

NOTE : Delete Data.txt for repeat usages!!!!!
